{
  "texts": [
    "The CC market has developed better over time, and market participants have become more experienced, suggesting that the efficiency level has gradually improved.",
    "Therefore, investigating the efficiency of the CC markets within a time-varying framework is crucial.",
    "Indeed, the CC market is very emotional, and investors in this market have a dynamic character, dealing with continuous and smooth changes in the behavior of CC prices.",
    "This feature can only be captured through analysis in a time-varying framework rather than splitting the period into sub-periods selected a priori.",
    "Modeling efficiency in a time-varying manner depicts market efficiency as a continuous process that depends on the market's conditions and events."
  ]
}